    <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-4">
      Maximize the value of your credit card rewards and airline loyalty points with our comprehensive converter tool. 
      Whether you're planning your next vacation or looking to optimize your reward strategy, this tool helps you 
      make informed decisions about your points and miles.
    </p>
    
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 my-6">
      <div class="bg-blue-50 p-4 rounded-sm">
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-blue-900 mb-2">üèÜ Key Features</h3>
